videos.description: Marlon Davidson gets the strip sack off Arkansas QB Ben Hicks to set up great field position for Auburn.
videos.headline: Davidson's strip sack sets up Auburn

videos.description: Bo Nix rushes four yards for a touchdown, giving Auburn an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Nix's TD run gives Auburn early lead

videos.description: Shaun Shivers barrels into the end zone for a six-yard touchdown as Auburn extends the lead to 14-0.
videos.headline: Shivers scores as Auburn adds to its lead

videos.description: Chandler Wooten intercepts Arkansas punter Sam Loy as Auburn looks to pad its lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn gets the INT on fake punt) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Auburn gets the INT on fake punt

videos.description: Arkansas WR Treylon Burks makes a terrific catch for the first down.
videos.headline: Burks makes sensational catch for Arkansas

videos.description: Bo Nix finds a wide-open Seth Williams for the 48-yard TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nix hits Williams for the score) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Nix hits Williams for the score

videos.description: Bo Nix throws a perfect pass to Anthony Schwartz for a 28-yard touchdown as Auburn pours it on.
videos.headline: Schwartz reels in the 28 yard TD

videos.description: Arkansas capitalizes on the Auburn turnover with the 45-yard TD pass to Cheyenne O'Grady.
videos.headline: Arkansas' first TD of the day comes on 45-yard pass
